 I've never seen before, and even further biting the guy who has the virus. Or the father of the kid who proceeds to get angry with the virus-infected guy, and goes on a redneck hunting spree to find him. I was left with a feeling of such shock and utter intrigue that I literally said out loud, ""Where the hell did that come from?""I just simply couldn't believe what I had seen. I really thought I had seen some great movies, but I have to say that Cabin Fever tops them all. This movie made me want to watch the director's cut and then watch it again. Then watch it with the commentary.Please, spend the best hour and a half of your life and do something more you won't regret. Watching this movie, perhaps."	1
